OL,3,CCompany fined #90,000 after worker
OL,4,Cdies from falling 20-feet through roof
OL,6,FA Black County company and its
OL,7,Foperation manager have both been fined
OL,8,Fafter a man fell to his death through
OL,9,Fa fragile roof.
OL,11,FMaciej Rozanski, 42, had been working
OL,12,Fto remove a redundant steel cleaning
OL,13,Fmachine from the Surface Technik (Old
OL,14,FHill) Limited's Sovereign Works site
OL,15,Fon Deepdale Lane in Dudley on 29 June
OL,16,F2018.
