OL,3,CCompany fined #90,000 after worker
OL,4,Cdies from falling 20-feet through roof
OL,6,FDuring the work, Mr Rozanski stepped
OL,7,Fonto a fragile roof and fell more than
OL,8,F20-feet to the floor. He suffered
OL,9,Fserious injuries and was pronounced
OL,10,Fdead at the scene.
OL,12,FFollowing an investigation by the
OL,13,FHealth and Safety Executive (HSE), the
OL,14,Fcompany, which is now in liquidation,
OL,15,Fwas found guilty following a trial
OL,16,Fearlier this week.
OL,18,FOperation manager Robert Hammond had
OL,19,Falready entered a guilty plea, but
OL,20,Fdenied he was responsible for health
OL,21,Fand safety at the site.
