OL,3,CCompany fined #90,000 after worker
OL,4,Cdies from falling 20-feet through roof
OL,6,FThe HSE investigation found that the
OL,7,Fcompany began the work to remove the
OL,8,Fmachinery in December 2017 and that
OL,9,Fproject was led by Robert Hammond.
OL,11,FOn the day of the incident, Mr
OL,12,FRozanski and another employee were
OL,13,Ftasked with dismantling and removing
OL,14,Fthe machine at the top of the tower.
OL,15,FIt was during this activity that Mr
OL,16,FRozanski fell to his death.
