OL,3,CCompany fined #90,000 after worker
OL,4,Cdies from falling 20-feet through roof
OL,6,FThe work to remove corrugated steel
OL,7,Fsheets from the disused tower was
OL,8,Fcarried out at height, near to a
OL,9,Ffragile roof surface without suitable
OL,10,Faccess equipment or safe working
OL,11,Fpractices.
OL,13,FThe investigation found there was no
OL,14,Fsuitable and sufficient risk
OL,15,Fassessment made for the work at height
OL,16,Factivities.
