OL,3,CCompany fined #90,000 after worker
OL,4,Cdies from falling 20-feet through roof
OL,6,F"This case highlights the risks of
OL,7,Fworking at height from or near to
OL,8,Ffragile roof surfaces and the
OL,9,Fimportance of a risk assessment,
OL,10,Fproper planning, training and
OL,11,Fsupervision of work at height and the
OL,12,Fuse of suitable access equipment to
OL,13,Fensure that the work can be carried
OL,14,Fout safely.
OL,16,F"It also demonstrates that placing a
OL,17,Fcompany into liquidation is no bar to
OL,18,Fprosecution."
